{"tid":1856544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救救前線救護！！","createTime":"2020-02-01T16:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:34:17.000Z","uid":316031,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0a44c9d0259272c41d841a2acea7d43ad84230","tid":1856544,"uid":316031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"（轉）<br />\n<br />\n我朋友做前線救護，做完一轉，點知隔日就話個人呈陽性反應，啲人上車又唔撚講自己返過大陸，完全冇防護衣，口罩又得一個，個頭將啲口罩鎖起晒，每次要配給咁，要換都唔得！<br />\n<br />\n朋友都已經返咗屋企，又同屋企兩老食飯。<strong>啱啱就派人去接我朋友去隔離！</strong><br />\n<br />\n你上車又唔撚講自己返過大陸，十個有八個都唔誠實申報，前線救護啲防護又唔夠，依家仲要中門大開！前線救護本來就高危，你啲仆街自私佬，仲有個7婆政府，你要幾多人幫你埋單！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFQ2wjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFQ2wjY.jpg&h=3567b10c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"850783ca89b3459204049da3776046bbc783ec97","tid":1856544,"uid":292739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"crazy government <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17371861d15c1f9caa2bd65beed5acb3541132ef","tid":1856544,"uid":81478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"支持醫護罷工 一日未全面封關都罷佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d96ac39981fdf10ae1a2537f51395582a7aa6c","tid":1856544,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"7989691e9fbdb118c8574b22ac06f15635fa8d6e","tid":1856544,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"罷工，等班番大陸既自私鬼等死"},{"pid":"a1420b23ba1507e9e960c2a81a2061517dfcdf3b","tid":1856544,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:47:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"663c83114750b5a36fba3307e99b58f6b2fe8a7b","tid":1856544,"uid":222360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:51:44.000Z","msg":"我好朋友做救護<br />